OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fsunny this evening and remaining
OL,7,Flargely dry overnight. Cloud tending
OL,8,Fto increase in many areas by morning,
OL,9,Fperhaps bringing a few spots of light
OL,10,Frain across the Pennines.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,13,Fsunshine, though perhaps the chance
OL,14,Ffor a little light rain on western
OL,15,Fhills at first. Feeling fresher
OL,16,Finland, but warmer at the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
