OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,6,Flargely sunny and warm or very warm on
OL,7,FSaturday. Trending cooler and more
OL,8,Fchangeable from Sunday. An increased
OL,9,Fchance of rain, but still some fine,
OL,10,Fwarm weather at times.
